go to settings ->sharing
click on screen sharing (enable it)
click on computer setting and check VNC viewer

then download VNCviewer in your Windows machine

type in the credentials to access to your mac
To know which user are you logged in:

whoami

Type the password you use to login and not the password that you can set in the Mac settings in the VNC option


don't install apple remote desktop in your mac
or vnc will go in conflict (just close apple remote deskotp)
